    parentName: "p"
  }, "Saito"), "\nHow do you ensure the credibility of the latest/updated information?"), mdx("p", null, mdx("strong", {
    parentName: "p"
  }, "Imai"), "\nRegarding updating the latest data, if you apply in one place, it will be verified for correctness and is reflected in other places. As far as the reliability of the information is concerned, it is an optional feature, but we have been developing a credit score about the reliability of providers since the very beginning of the release."), mdx("p", null, mdx("strong", {
