    parentName: "p"
  }, "Inamura"), "\nThere are two different discussions: sharing of My Number and sharing personal information linked to My Number. I think the revision of the law about sharing personal data related to My Number is challenging. This is because sharing with the private sector, the information collected by the government will require amendment. But, since elections are a duty of government, the compatibility of My Number information is useful."), mdx("h2", {
